{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.240", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.960", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.200", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Heute hat der Deutsche Bundestag mit seiner inhaltlichen Arbeit in der 19.\u00a0Legislaturperiode begonnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.880", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Heute beginnt damit auch eine Zeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.800", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in der Debatten \u00fcber alternativloses Abwirtschaften unseres Landes der Vergangenheit angeh\u00f6ren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.240", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir fordern hiermit die Bundesregierung auf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.480", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unverz\u00fcglich alternative ordnungs- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.680", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und handelspolitische Rahmenbedingungen zu setzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.160", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die in Zukunft internationale Fusionen zum Nachteil des Standortes Deutschland unterbinden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.760", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist f\u00fcr die AfD-Fraktion ein unertr\u00e4glicher Zustand, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.920", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir uns im Bundestag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.040", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gerade einmal zwei Wochen nach Bekanntwerden der Paradise Papers, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.920", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nun mit einem industriellen Urgestein Deutschlands, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.400", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der thyssenkrupp\u00a0AG, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.160", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "besch\u00e4ftigen m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.680", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das sich ebenfalls in die Steuervermeidungsoase Niederlande absetzen m\u00f6chte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.160", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und es ist geradezu ein Skandal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.280", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die mittlerweile gr\u00f6\u00dfte Oppositionspartei, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.400", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die SPD, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.720", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Zuge ihrer heute beantragten Ma\u00dfnahmen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.800", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in ihrer Rede vielleicht schon, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.040", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber nicht bei ihren Ma\u00dfnahmen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.240", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diese aktuelle Steuerflucht mit keinem Wort aufgreift."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.720", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Stattdessen kramen Sie lieber in der Mottenkiste des Montan-Mitbestimmungsgesetzes aus dem Jahre\u00a01951 und verweisen auf einen fast zwei Jahre alten Antrag der GroKo zur angeblichen St\u00e4rkung der Stahlindustrie in Deutschland und Europa. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.680", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wohin uns dieser Antrag gebracht hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.760", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sehen wir doch an der heutigen Debatte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.440", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine sehr geehrten Damen und Herren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.600", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Welch eine politische Bankrotterkl\u00e4rung!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.880", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nachdem die SPD in den letzten 19\u00a0Jahren 15\u00a0Jahre an der Regierung war, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.880", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat sie nicht nur die dringend notwendige Steuerharmonisierung in Europa verschlafen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.480", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern ihre Art der politischen Unterst\u00fctzung hat ganz offenbar dazu gef\u00fchrt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.520", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass ein ehemaliger Stahltitan wie thyssenkrupp nun auf internationale Hilfe durch eine Fusion angewiesen ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.800", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Angesichts Ihrer verfehlten Standort- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.760", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Industrie\u00adpolitik haben wir auch Verst\u00e4ndnis f\u00fcr ein fusionierendes Unternehmen wie thyssenkrupp, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.800", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das sich seit Jahren der unfairen und staatlich massiv subventionierten Konkurrenz aus China ausgesetzt sieht und sich mit anderen Wettbewerbern daher zusammenschlie\u00dfen muss."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.720", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber auch zum Fusionspartner Tata und zum ebenfalls indischen Stahlgiganten Mittal stellen wir der Bundesregierung die Fragen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.480", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie steht es eigentlich mit Subventionen und Protektionismus in Indien? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.680", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wird die deutsche Industrie auch gegen diese Konkurrenten wieder von der Bundesregierung im Stich gelassen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.760", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihr ganz offensichtlich erfolgloser Ma\u00dfnahmenkatalog, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.920", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Sie jetzt nach zwei Jahren wieder aufw\u00e4rmen wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.040", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "w\u00fcrde genau dazu f\u00fchren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.760", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Um das zu verhindern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.240", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "fordern wir das Schlie\u00dfen internationaler Steuerschlupfl\u00f6cher, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.560", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "WTO-konforme Schutzinstrumente f\u00fcr einen fairen internationalen Handel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.760", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die internationale Angleichung von umweltrechtlichen Auflagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.120", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine vorausschauende und nachhaltige Standort- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.480", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Industriepolitik zur Vermeidung von Entlassungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.120", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und vor allem muss der Know-how-Abfluss aus Deutschland endlich gestoppt werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.560", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Stattdessen f\u00fchrt jedoch eine von Ihnen gr\u00fcn\u00e4ugig entworfene und von einem SPD-gef\u00fchrten Ministerium dilettantisch umgesetzte Energiewende dazu, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.680", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass ein weiterer Industriegigant\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.280", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich spreche hier von Siemens, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.000", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dar\u00fcber haben wir heute schon einmal gesprochen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.600", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vor einem massiven Stellenabbau steht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.960", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und auch hier haben Sie mit Ihrer heutigen Aktuellen Stunde medienwirksam so getan, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.520", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als ob Sie den Arbeitnehmern beispringen wollten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.800", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gerade so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.200", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als w\u00e4ren Sie und Ihre Wirtschaftsminister in den letzten Jahren nicht f\u00fcr die Industrie- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "279.200", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Energiepolitik in diesem Land verantwortlich gewesen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "279.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "282.920", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie auch schon beim Ausverkauf von Nokia, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "282.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "294.000", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mannesmann oder H\u00f6chst sehen wir bei der SPD wieder nur das Vergie\u00dfen von Kroko-Tr\u00e4nen und die nachtr\u00e4glichen Versuche, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "294.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "296.440", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an Symptomen herumzudoktern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "296.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "298.800", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "anstatt eine vorausschauende Standort- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "298.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "301.000", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Industriepolitik zu betreiben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "301.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "305.240", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren Kollegen von der SPD, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "305.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "310.800", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben sich gestern gegen eine erneute Gro\u00dfe Koalition ausgesprochen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "310.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "312.040", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Richtig so! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "312.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "319.360", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bitte bleiben Sie angesichts Ihrer Regierungsbilanz in der Wirtschaftspolitik auch in Zukunft in der Opposition."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "319.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "320.840", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "N\u00e4chster Redner, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "320.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "322.480", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ebenfalls erste Rede: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "322.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "333.000", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kollege Bernd Reuther von der FDP-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
}